title: So You Think You Can Dance Australia Season 4
description:
From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia:

Season four of "So You Think You Can Dance Australia", the Australian version of the American reality dance-off series "So You Think You Can Dance", was hosted by Carrie Bickmore with Paula Abdul, Shannon Holtzapffel, Jason Gilkison and Aaron Cash acting as the judges. Auditions for the fourth season were held between September and October 2013 in Perth, Brisbane, Melbourne, Adelaide and Sydney. The TV show premiered on 9 February 2014 and the last show was on 1 May 2014
